txt.en: 'Yes, yes, what can I do for you?'
'You look like a traveller...if you ever find yourself in Buckland, you remind my no-good cousin Hodric he owes me money!'
'I hear there's going to be another big gathering at the party tree soon. Nothing will top old Baggins's Party though.'
'Nothing is quite as pleasant as a nice pipe of Old Toby.'
